   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:39,892:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: handler to miss closing LONG positions on new inverse ETPs during a DOWN-to-UP flip.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:39,893:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Impact
