   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:40,112:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  field to the KillSwitch
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:40,113:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: class for audit purposes.
