   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:42,189:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: SECTION 2: THE VANGUARD SNIPER — Fund-First Dual-Blade
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:42,189:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Execution Engine
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:42,190:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: The Vanguard Sniper is the beating heart of the NZT-48 system. It answers two questions with absolute precision: 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:42,190:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: WHAT
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:42,191:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  do we trade, and 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:42,191:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: WHEN
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:42,201:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  do we pull the trigger. Every other module — macro intelligence, volume profiling,
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:42,203:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: risk management — exists to serve this single decision function. One signal. One trade. One day at a time. That is how
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:42,203:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: GBP 10,000 becomes GBP 1.49 million.
