   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:43,218:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     Global cross-asset RVOL anomaly scanner.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:43,219:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     Feeds high-conviction discoveries to S15 via ISA Priority
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:43,219:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Mapping.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:43,219:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     Scans 200-500 pre-filtered tickers every 30 minutes +
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:43,220:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: trigger-based.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:43,220:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     References:
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:43,220:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         - Chordia & Swaminathan (2000): lead-lag from trading
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:43,221:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: volume
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:43,221:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         - Llorente et al. (2002): informed trading and
