   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:43,222:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         - Karpoff (1987): relation between price changes and volume
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:43,222:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     """
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:43,223:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     def __init__(
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:43,223:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         self,
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:43,224:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         watchlist: List[str],           # 200-500 tickers,
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:43,224:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: refreshed daily
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:43,225:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         regime_provider: RegimeProvider, # HMM regime from
