   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:43,581:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: min
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:43,582:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  (market hours) | Scheduled Scan | 200-500 watchlist | 1-min OHLCV | 10 batches x 50 tickers. Takes ~2-3
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:43,583:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: minutes. |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:43,583:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:43,584:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | | | | | Compute: real-time RVOL, VWAP, Z-score |
