   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:44,216:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 35/65 | 1.99% | 14,289% | +0.30%
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:44,216:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:44,217:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:44,217:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:44,218:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 33/67 (v13.0)
