   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:44,220:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:44,220:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: +0.27%
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:44,220:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:44,221:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
