   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:44,929:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: *
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:44,930:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  f
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:44,930:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: *
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:44,931:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:44,932:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 0.3 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:44,933:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: *
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:44,933:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  f
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:44,934:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: *
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:44,935:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Unchanged. Strong downtrend. Same as RANGE
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:44,936:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: _
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:44,938:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: BOUND -- the system
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:44,938:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: should be very cautious. |
