   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,795:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Tier 1: £10K - £100K (Current Phase)
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,795:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,796:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Constraint
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,796:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: : None. Full access to all 12 ISA ETPs.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,797:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
