   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,797:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: : 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,797:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: <
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,798:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  0.5% of ADV on any single instrument.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,798:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,798:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Execution
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,799:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: : Market orders acceptable. Impact is noise-level.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,799:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
