   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,800:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: : None. Focus on strategy refinement and track record building.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,800:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Tier 2: £100K - £500K
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,801:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
