   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,801:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: : Beginning to appear on market maker radar for lowest-volume ETPs.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,802:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
