   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,804:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: : Limit orders preferred. Monitor fill rates for slippage.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,804:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
