   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,806:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: .
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,807:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Diversify signal allocation across more tickers to avoid concentration.
