   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,808:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: : Single-ticker positions become market-moving on thin ETPs.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,808:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,809:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Participation rate
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:45,809:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: : 3-10% of ADV if concentrated.
