   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,095:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 3R, crash detection, API failure, cascade halt, state divergence | Instant | Unlimited | YES (alarm) |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,096:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
