   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,100:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: stop hit, regime change, liquidity wall warning | Instant (silent) | 5/day, then batch | No |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,100:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,100:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,100:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: P2
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,102:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | New signal,
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,103:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: graduation event, A/B team change, backup success | 30-min batch | 10/day | No |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,103:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,103:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,104:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: P3
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,106:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Pattern statistics, SHAP
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,106:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: drift, macro summary, ML health | 2x daily digest | 2/day | No |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,107:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: P0 Events (Never Suppressed)
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,107:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Event | Message Template |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,107:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,108:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |-------|-----------------|
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,108:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,108:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Daily DD > 2% | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,109:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: P0 HALT: Daily drawdown {dd}%
