   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,110:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,111:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Weekly DD > 5% | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,112:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: P0 HALT: Weekly
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,112:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: drawdown {dd}% exceeds 5% limit. All entries suspended until Monday.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,113:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,113:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,114:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Total DD >
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,114:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 10% | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,115:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: P0 EMERGENCY: Total drawdown {dd}%. Approaching 15% hard stop. Manual
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,115:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: review required.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,116:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,116:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,116:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Cascade halt (R-10) | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,117:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: P0 CASCADE: {n} stops in {m} minutes. 30-min
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,117:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: cool-down active.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,118:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,118:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,118:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Docker restart | 
