   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,120:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,120:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,120:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | API failure | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,121:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: P0 INFRA: {api_name} API failed {n}
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,122:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: consecutive times. Last error: {err}.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,122:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,123:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,123:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | State divergence | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,124:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: P0 INFRA: Redis/SQLite
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,125:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: state divergence on key {key}. SQLite value used.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,125:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,125:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,126:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Backup failure | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,126:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: P0 INFRA: S3
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,127:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: backup failed. Last successful backup: {timestamp}.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,127:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,128:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Correlation Escalation
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,128:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Rule
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,130:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: : If 3 or more P1 events fire within any 15-minute window, all subsequent events in that window are
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,130:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: automatically escalated to P0.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,130:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Rationale
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,135:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: : Multiple simultaneous P1 events (e.g., stop hit + regime change + liquidity warning) indicate a systemic
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,135:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: event, not independent occurrences. The combination is more dangerous than any individual event.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,136:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Implementation
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,136:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: :
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,137:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: class NotificationEscalator:
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,137:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     def __init__(self):
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,138:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         self.p1_timestamps = deque(maxlen=100)
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,138:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     def should_escalate(self) -> bool:
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,138:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         now = datetime.utcnow()
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,139:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         window = timedelta(minutes=15)
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,140:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         recent = [t for t in self.p1_timestamps if now - t <
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,140:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: window]
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,141:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         return len(recent) >= 3
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,141:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     def notify(self, priority: str, message: str):
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,142:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         if priority == "P1":
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,142:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:             self.p1_timestamps.append(datetime.utcnow())
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,143:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:             if self.should_escalate():
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,143:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:                 priority = "P0"
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,144:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:                 message = f"[ESCALATED from P1] {message}"
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,144:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         send_telegram(priority=priority, message=message)
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,145:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Weekly Report (Sunday 20:00 UK)
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,145:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Delivered as a single Telegram message every Sunday at 20:00 UK time. Contains:
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,146:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  1 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,147:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Win Rate by Strategy
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,147:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: : S15 WR, overall WR, WR by regime
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,148:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  2 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,148:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Win Rate by Regime
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,148:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: : Bull/Cautious/Crisis breakdowns
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,149:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  3 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,149:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Dry Days
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,149:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: : Number of days with zero entries (and why — no signal vs. halted)
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:46,150:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  4 
