   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:47,356:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: : Allows larger bets in TRENDING
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:47,357:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: _
