   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:47,358:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  3 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:47,359:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: TRENDING
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:47,359:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: _
