   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:47,433:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | -0.405%          |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:47,433:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:47,433:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
