   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:47,436:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:       |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:47,437:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:47,441:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 35% / 65%          | +1.53%
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:47,442:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:      | 1.13%   | 1.35   | +1.038%             | -0.400%          |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:47,442:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
