   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:47,494:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:    | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:47,495:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: +3bp
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:47,495:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:47,496:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: The 33/67 split is 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:47,497:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: robust across regimes
   DEBUG: 2026-03-04 16:39:47,498:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: , with worst-case underperformance of only 3bp vs. regime-optimal splits.
